---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Payment Gateway - The Davinci Project" description="Accept digital asset payments securely and efficiently.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Payment Gateway</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Accept digital asset payments securely and efficiently with our escrow-powered gateway.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Choose Our Payment Gateway?</h2>
      <p>Our payment gateway combines the security of blockchain escrow with the ease of traditional payment processing. Merchants can accept digital asset payments while buyers enjoy the protection of our escrow protocol.</p>
      
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Multi-cryptocurrency support</li>
        <li>Instant settlement options</li>
        <li>Escrow protection for buyers and sellers</li>
        <li>Real-time exchange rate conversion</li>
        <li>Automated invoicing and receipts</li>
        <li>Fraud prevention and risk management</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Integration</h2>
      <p>Our payment gateway integrates seamlessly with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>E-commerce platforms (Shopify, WooCommerce, Magento)</li>
        <li>Custom websites via REST API</li>
        <li>Mobile applications via SDK</li>
        <li>Point-of-sale systems</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Start accepting crypto payments today</h3>
        <p>Get set up in minutes and start accepting digital asset payments.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .content-section p, .content-section li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .content-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  
  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-green);
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
